data.description: Sought after Rocky Point pool home with backyard oasis. This four large bedroom, three bath, open kitchen area with a separate family and living area situated on a large fenced in corner lot with a new saltwater pool, metal roof, and AC. All the big-ticket items are already completed for the new owners within the past couple years.... Other important features include a full home generator with a five-hundred-gallon propane tank, outside shower with hot/cold water (oasis) and an oversized detached concrete garage with eight-foot entrance door and high ceilings that can double as a shop or an abundant storage area (can fit RV or Boat)! The property has ample space for RV/boat storage along with plenty of room for the daily automobiles. Steps away from Maggy's Hammock Park, as well as Twin Rivers Park and waterfront dining/shopping. This one will not disappoint!
